FBIS4-21778 "jptot014__l94078" JPRS-TOT-94-014-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 29 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Arabs Attack Israeli in Petah Tiqva Arabs Attack Israeli in Petah Tiqva `In Serious State' TA2903093894 Tel Aviv IDF Radio in Hebrew 0930 GMT 29 Mar 94 TA2903093894 Tel Aviv IDF Radio Hebrew BFN [Text] An Israeli who was attacked in Petah Tiqva continues to be in serious condition. Our initial information is that at around 1030 this morning a man was attacked with an ax by two Arab construction workers in downtown Petah Tiqva. He was seriously injured in the head. The assailants fled the scene and have not yet been caught.
